quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  40,41,Kananjalo Hini na bantu bakuthi kwenzeka njani na ukuba ndithi ndinimemela elusindisweni nibe nina nindimemela eMlilweni
  40,42,"Nina nindimemela ekubeni ndingakholwa kuAllâh nasekubeni ndayamanise endingenalwazi ngako kuYe, Mna ke ndinimemela kuSobunganga, uMxoleli"
  40,43,Oko nina nindimemela kuko akunayo (impendulo) xa kucelwa (kuko) kweli hlabathi nakwelizayo; ukanti kukuAllâh apho ukubuyela kwethu kukhoyo yaye inene abagabadeli baya kuba ngamadlelane oMlilo
  40,44,"Kanti ke niya kukukhumbula endikutshoyo kuni, yaye ndibeka ithemba lam kuAllâh. Inene uAllâh nguMjongi wezicaka zaKhe"
  40,45,Ke kaloku uAllâh Wamkhusela kumayelenqe angcolileyo ababewaqulunqile baza abantu bakwaFir’awn bagutyungelwa ngesona sibi isohlwayo
  40,46,"UMlilo; bagagana nawo ekuseni nangokuhlwa3. Kanti ngoMhla iMini yoVuko ivela (kuya kuthiwa): “Phosani (phakathi eMlilweni) abantu bakwaFir’awn bangene kwesona sohlwayo sibuhlungu.”"
  40,47,"Yabona! Baya kuphikisana phakathi eMlilweni, ababebuthathaka baya kuthi kwabo babekhukhumele: “Inene thina sasingabalandeli benu, ingaba niza kusiphumza, nithabathe (esenu) isabelo soMlilo na?’’"
  40,48,"Abo babekhukhumele baya kuthi: “Inene, sisonke sikuwo nathi Inene uAllâh Ugwebile phakathi kwezicaka zaKhe.’’"
  40,49,"Abo baseMlilweni baya kuthi kubagcini besiHogo: Celani eNkosini yenu ukuba isinciphisele ngemini enye kwisohlwayo.’’"
  40,50,"Baya kuthi: “Akuzanga kufike baThunywa nemiqondiso ecacileyo na kuni? Baya kuthi bona: “Ewe.’’ Baya kuphendula, “Ziceleleni nina (ngokwenu) kodwa isicelo sabangakholwayo asinto yanto ngaphandle kokuba kukulahleka”"
  40,51,Inene Thina Siya kubenza babe noloyiso abaThunywa bethu nabo bakholwayo ngoku besesemhlabeni kanti nangeMini amangqina aya kumiswa
  40,52,"NgeMini ukuzithethelela kwabo kungayi kubanceda abenzi bobugwenxa, yaye baya kuba nesiqalekiso, nelona khaya lakha lalibi (esiHogweni)"
  40,53,Kananjalo Thina Sanika uMûsâ isiKhokelo Senza aBantwana bakwaSirayeli baba ziindlalifa zesiBhalo
  40,54,Ukuba sibe sisiKhokelo nesikhumbuzi kwabo bangabokuqiqa
  40,55,"Ngoko ke wena (Muhammad) yiba nomonde, inene isithembiso sika-Allâh siyinyaniso, ucele itarhu lesono4 sakho, uzukise (uAllâh) ngendumiso yeNkosi ngokuhlwa nasekuseni"
  40,56,"Inene abo baphikisanayo ngokuphathelene nemiqondiso ka- Allâh bengenagunya lifikileyo kubo – akukho nto ezifubeni zabo ngaphandle kwenkukhumalo (bona ubuProfeti) asokuze babufumane. Ke wena funa ukhuseleko ngoAllâh, inene yena nguYe OnguSokuva, uSokubona"
  40,57,"Ukudalwa kwamazulu nomhlaba kukhulu ngenene kunokudalwa kwabantu: kodwa uninzi lwabantu alwazi"
  40,58,"Kanti abalingani abaziimfama nababonayo, (bengalingani kananjalo) abo bakholwayo, benza ubulungisa nabo benza ukungcola, kuncinane enikuqaphelayo"
  40,59,"Inene iYure iyeza yona, akukho ntandabuzo ngayo, kodwa abantu abaninzi abakholwa"
  40,60,"Ke kaloku iNkosi yakho Ithi: “Cela kuM; Ndiya kukuphendula Mna. Inene abo bakucekisayo ukunqulwa kwaM baya kungena esiHogweni bedelekile.”"
  40,61,NguAllâh Owanenzela ubusuku ukuze niphumle ngabo nemini (ukuba) ininike ukubona. Inene uAllâh nguMnini- Bubele eluntwini. Kodwa uninzi lwabantu alunambulelo
  40,62,"NguAllâh ke loWo, iNkosi yakho, uMdali wezinto zonke; akukho thixo wumbi ngaphandle kwaKhe, kanti nimfamekiseke njani na"
  40,63,"(Nabangaphambili) kunani baya bamfamekiseka ngolo hlobo, besala iiVesi zika-Allâh"
  40,64,"NguAllâh Onenzele umhlaba waba yindawo yokuzinza nesibhakabhaka saba luphahla, Wanibumba, Wanifezekisela izimo zenu Wanibonelela ngezinto ezilungileyo. NguAllâh ke loWo, iNkosi yenu; Usikelelekile uAllâh iNkosi, uMlondolozi wamaphakade.’’"
  40,65,"Yena Uphila ngonaphakade, akukho thixo wumbi ngaphandle kwaKhe, ngoko thandazani kuYe, ninyanisekile kuYe enkolweni, iindumiso zonke mazibe kuAllâh iNkosi yamaphakade"